					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Get a better external enclosure.  Some of them just suck, and should not be used at all.  I've made the mistake of just buying the cheapest one.<br />And if the external hard drive does not have a reliable connection, you need to force Windows to NEVER try to defrag the drive, otherwise you can lose everything during a botched defrag.</div>

					
