					<td class="gensmall" width="100%"><div style="float: left;">&nbsp;<b>Post subject:</b> <a href="#p215969">Re: External USB Drive Interrupted When Trying to Format</a></div><div style="float: right;"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=215969#p215969"><img src="./styles/subsilver2/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a><b>Posted:</b> Thu Mar 29, 2018 5:31 pm&nbsp;</div></td>
